title: Solomon - Brahms No.2 & Tchaikovsky No.1 Piano Concertos - TQMP
description:
[b]ENJOY ...... :o   :o  [/b]

This is the fifth of seven CDs from Solomon being uploaded this week.

All from the EMI Classics Range with .pdf insert in English, French & German.

This is CD5  -

Brahms: Piano Concerto No. 2 in B flat Op. 83 (2008 Digital Remaster)

I. Allegro non troppo
II. Allegro appassionato
III. Andante
IV. Allegretto grazioso

Tchaikovsky: Piano Concerto No. 1 in B flat minor Op. 23 (2008 Digital Remaster)

I. Allegro non troppo e molto maestoso - Allegro con spirito
II. Andantino semplice - Prestissimo - Tempo I
III. Allegro con fuoco
